<h3>演示如何访问滑块控件</h3>

<input type="range" id="myRange">

<p>点击按钮来获得滑块控件的值。</p>

<button onclick="myFunction()">试一下</button>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
function myFunction() {
    var x = document.getElementById("myRange").value;
    document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = x;
}
</script>

